<h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">About this catalogue</h1>


<iframe style="margin-bottom: 3rem;" width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zZI04ZlEgnM?si=QxPqzf0GJC1Vc0gg" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
  
<p >This site provides a browseable catalogue of AI tools being used in the public sector.<p>

<p>It was built by <a href="https://www.peterkappus.com/?utm_source=aitools" class="govuk-link">Peter Kappus</a> using data scraped from the public internet, cleaned, and published by the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/government-digital-service">Government Digital Service (GDS)</a> via their experimental <a href="https://cddo-af.data.gov.uk/other/public_access/ai_tools_catalogue/AI-tools-catalogue-pilot.html" target="_blank" class="govuk-link">AI Tools Knowledge Graph</a>.</p>

<p>Read the <a href="https://www.peterkappus.com/blog/building-a-public-sector-ai-tools-catalogue-with-cursor/">blog post</a> to learn how I made it.</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m" id="disclaimer">DISCLAIMER</h2>

<p>This site was developed independently of and is not in any way affiliated with or endorsed by GDS, DSIT, or any other government entity.</p>

<p>It is provided AS-IS with no warranty or guarantee of any kind. Data may not be 100% accurate and should always be verified by visiting the source URL for any tool.</p>

<p>In no event shall Peter Kappus, PNK Industries Limited, GDS, or anyone else be held responsible for any losses suffered as a result of using this site. You agree to use this site and data at your own risk.</p>


<H2 class="govuk-heading-m" id="cookies">Cookies</h2>
<p >This site uses <a href="https://developers.google.com/analytics">Google Analytics (GA)</a> to help me measure traffic and understand how I can improve it. GA uses <a href="https://support.google.com/analytics/answer/11397207?hl=en">these cookies</a> to function.</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Accessibility</h2>
<p >This service is designed to meet WCAG 2.2 AA.</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Feedback welcome!</h2>
<p >Please direct all queries to <a href="https://www.peterkappus.com/contact">Peter Kappus</a>.</p>

